name: ProduceChecker
0:
”Alexa, open produce checker”
”Alexa, ask produce checker about 4020”
”Alexa, ask produce checker what is the PLU code 4011”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: produce checker
des: PLU codes administered by the International Federation for Produce Standards (IFPS) are 4 or 5 digit identification numbers affixed to a produce in grocery stores The PLU number identifies produce items based upon various attributes which can include the commodity, the variety, the growing methodology (e.g. organic) and the size group. This skill helps you to find the details of a produce by asking its PLU code. All results are based on the data available on the IFPS website as on 7/6/2017
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
